{"type":"message","id":"a181f52b","parentId":"c5edcec4","timestamp":"2026-03-15T21:40:43.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以使用的哦~ 😊 我看到`C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\skills`下面已经安装了这些技能：\n\n📦 **已安装技能列表：**\n- agent-browser (AI智能浏览器控制)\n- copywriting (文案写作)\n- find-skills (技能搜索)\n- free-ride (免费AI模型管理)\n- frontend-design (前端设计)\n- git-hub (GitHub集成)\n- humanizer (AI写作人性化)\n- model-usage (模型使用统计)\n- n8n (工作流自动化)\n- playwright-scraper (网页爬虫)\n- ppt-generator (PPT生成)\n- self-optimization (自我优化)\n- skill-creator (技能创建指南)\n- skill-vetting (技能安全审核)\n- slack (Slack控制)\n- summarize (内容摘要)\n- tavily-search (Tavily专业搜索)\n- ui-ux-pro-max (UI/UX设计)\n- using-superpowers (技能高级使用)\n- vercel-react-best-practices (Vercel React最佳实践)\n- web-search-exa (Exa神经网络搜索)\n- youtube-watcher (YouTube字幕提取)\n\n还有你自己加的咸鱼发布技能哦~ 🐟 技能只要放在这个目录下，按照规则配置好，我就能读取它的`SKILL.md`然后使用啦~ 你是想使用哪个技能，还是遇到什么问题了呀？ 💡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773610838870}}
