{"type":"message","id":"51f59ec3","parentId":"80c62bf2","timestamp":"2026-03-15T21:42:21.733Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ruws9n68rd24oe36sj2fxo9b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\nxiaohongshu-mcp  Xiaohongshu (小红书) Automation\nSummary: Automate Xiaohongshu (RedNote) content operations using a Python client for the xiaohongshu-mcp server. Use for: (1) Publishing image, text, and video content, (2) Searching for notes and trends, (3) Analyzing post details and comments, (4) Managing user profiles and content feeds. Triggers: xiaohongshu automation, rednote content, publish to xiaohongshu, xiaohongshu search, social media management.\nOwner: Borye\nCreated: 2026-02-01T09:35:39.127Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-15T03:15:00.377Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1620,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nxiaohongshu-mcp  Xiaohongshu (小红书) Automation\nSummary: Automate Xiaohongshu (RedNote) content operations using a Python client for the xiaohongshu-mcp server. Use for: (1) Publishing image, text, and video content, (2) Searching for notes and trends, (3) Analyzing post details and comments, (4) Managing user profiles and content feeds. Triggers: xiaohongshu automation, rednote content, publish to xiaohongshu, xiaohongshu search, social media management.\nOwner: Borye\nCreated: 2026-02-01T09:35:39.127Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-15T03:15:00.377Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0","cwd":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_robot_01"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773610941732}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b84d45b","parentId":"51f59ec3","timestamp":"2026-03-15T21:42:26.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 找到啦！帮你搜到了几个适合管理咸鱼和小红书的技能哦~ 😊\n\n### 🐟 **咸鱼相关技能**\n\n**1. xianyu-auto-reply - 闲鱼自动回复助手** ⭐\n- **功能**：配置并运行闲鱼消息自动回复服务，只需要提供浏览器Cookie，就能后台持续监听消息，用AI智能回复买家\n- **适用场景**：自动客服、消息监控、挂机回复\n- **作者**：sinabs，最近更新：2026-03-15\n- **正好匹配你想要的自动化客服需求呢！**\n\n**2. xianyufilter - 闲鱼商品精选助手**\n- **功能**：自动严格筛选闲鱼个人闲置商品，排除商家，按价格区间筛选，输出价格升序前十\n- **适用场景**：竞品监控、价格搜索\n\n### 📕 **小红书相关技能**\n\n**xiaohongshu-mcp - 小红书自动化工具** ⭐\n- **功能**：\n  - 发布图片、文字、视频内容\n  - 搜索笔记和热门趋势\n  - 分析帖子详情和评论\n  - 管理用户资料和内容流\n- **适用场景**：内容发布、数据分析、账号管理\n- **作者**：Borye，最近更新：2026-03-15\n\n---\n\n### 💡 我的建议给主人：\n\n**方案1：安装 `xianyu-auto-reply`** - 最适合你现在的需求，正好是闲鱼自动回复，能帮你实现自动化客服，匹配你想做的消息监控+自动回复功能 ✅\n\n**方案2：同时安装 `xianyu-auto-reply` + `xiaohongshu-mcp`** - 咸鱼+小红书两个平台都覆盖，完整管理你的电商业务 📈\n\n**方案3：先不安装，继续用你自己写的xianyu-publish技能** - 你已经有一个咸鱼发布的技能了，可以先完善现有的，需要了再装新的 😊\n\n你想安装哪个技能呀？还是都安装？我帮你一键安装哦~ 🐱💰"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773610941733}}
