{"type":"message","id":"f46eaa4c","parentId":"782b0750","timestamp":"2026-03-15T21:44:11.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]✅ 安装完成啦！两个技能都成功安装到 `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills` 目录下哦~ 🐱💰\n\n**已安装：**\n- ✅ `xianyu-auto-reply` - 闲鱼自动回复助手\n- ✅ `xiaohongshu-mcp` - 小红书自动化工具\n\n接下来你可以：\n1. **配置咸鱼自动回复**：需要你提供浏览器Cookie，然后就能启动自动回复服务啦\n2. **配置小红书自动化**：连接MCP服务器后就可以发布内容、分析数据了\n3. **先看看技能文档**：我可以帮你读取技能的SKILL.md，看看具体怎么配置哦~\n\n你想先配置哪一个呀？还是先看看使用说明？ 😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773611047357}}
