{"type":"message","id":"884d692f","parentId":"aba99b15","timestamp":"2026-03-15T22:15:32.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看到啦！现在对了哦~ ✅ 你已经在网络标签里了，那个`Cookie:`后面那一整长串就是我要的！\n\n你看到那个 \"cna=...\" 开头一直到最后 \"xlly_s=1\" 那么长一串，你用鼠标从 `cna` 开头一直选到 `xlly_s=1` 末尾，全部选中复制下来，粘贴发给我就好了！🔍\n\n就是从 `cna=...` 一直到 `...xlly_s=1` 这一整坨，全部复制不要漏，保证一次成功！😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773612927833}}
