{"type":"message","id":"e3fda958","parentId":"39ffac52","timestamp":"2026-03-15T22:17:10.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还不够哦主人~ 😂 你只复制了开头两个，还要继续往后复制！那一整行很长的，你用鼠标拖动一直选到最末尾，全部都要复制哦~\n\n你看截图里，Cookie那一栏内容很长很长，需要把全部内容都复制下来。你可以：\n1. 点击Cookie那一行的值，然后按 `Ctrl+A` 全选\n2. 再按 `Ctrl+C` 复制\n3. 发给我就好啦\n\n这样就不会漏啦~ 🐱"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773613025865}}
