{"type":"message","id":"e13d8759","parentId":"2f5c6de5","timestamp":"2026-03-16T00:22:43.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还是一样的风控提示呢... 😔 \"哎哟喂,被挤爆啦,请稍后重试\"\n\n这个说明现在确实是被限流风控了，我给你几个方案：\n\n---\n\n### 方案1：**等待一段时间** ⏳（推荐）\n现在闲鱼明显限流了，让我们等它1-2个小时，风控自动解除后再启动，成功率会高很多。\n\n### 方案2：**浏览器手动操作一遍** 🖱️\n你现在打开浏览器：\n1. 访问 https://www.goofish.com\n2. 登录后点击「消息」，看看会不会弹出验证\n3. 如果有滑块验证，手动拖动完成\n4. 然后刷新页面，重新复制一份新的Cookie给我，我更新配置再试\n\n### 方案3：**换个浏览器或者清除缓存** 🔄\n- 如果你用的是Chrome，试试Edge\n- 或者清除一下浏览器缓存和Cookie，重新登录闲鱼再复制\n- 也可以试试隐私窗口登录\n\n---\n\n你想先试哪个？我建议先放一放，等几个小时再试，让闲鱼的风控冷静一下~ 🐱"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773620554497}}
{"type":"message","id":"276343e6","parentId":"e13d8759","timestamp":"2026-03-16T00:30:07.674Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5440be155cacc4eb24714e679b9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 08:30 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5440be155cacc4eb24714e679b9]\nou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b: 将咸鱼自动回复助手的skill内容总结一下发给我"}],"timestamp":1773621007669}}
